A small, simple IRC-like chat, encrypted with AES (using PolarSSL)


Compiling
---------
	$ make


Usage
-----
Add users to the password file using
	$ ./adduser <password FILE> <username> <password>

Run the server, providing the port, AES-key and password file as arguments
	$ ./server <port> <key> <password FILE>

Connect to the server from multiple clients
(Users should be added to the server password file in advanced)
	$ ./client <host> <port> <key> <username> <password>
